OL,3,CFirst Indian Hindu temple opens in
OL,4,CStoke-on-Trent
OL,6,FStoke-on-Trent's first Indian Hindu
OL,7,Ftemple officially opens today.
OL,9,FThe temple, or Mandir, is on the site
OL,10,Fof the Hindu Community Centre on Bold
OL,11,FStreet in the Hanley area of the city.
OL,13,FDr Chandra Cheruvu, chair of Hindu
OL,14,FCultural Society in Stoke-on-Trent
OL,15,Fsaid it's been a dream for the
OL,16,Fcommunity to have a temple, ever since
OL,17,FIndian Hindus moved to the
OL,18,FStaffordshire area approximately 50
OL,19,Fyears ago.
