OL,3,CFirst Indian Hindu temple opens in
OL,4,CStoke-on-Trent
OL,6,F"Fortunately, for the last few years,
OL,7,Fit took eight years to come to this
OL,8,Fstage, we bought the building in 2016,
OL,9,Fand there's been a lot of hard work.
OL,11,F"You can see the beautiful domes and
OL,12,Fstructures, all been made in India and
OL,13,Fbrought here. And it's basically to
OL,14,Fbring all cultures and people together.
OL,16,FCommittee members of the society said
OL,17,Fthey raised the money in one week,
OL,18,Fafter the site was available for
OL,19,Fauction, all from donations from
OL,20,Fmembers of the congregation.
