OL,3,CFirst Indian Hindu temple opens in
OL,4,CStoke-on-Trent
OL,6,FThe domes and structures in the temple
OL,7,Fwere made in India and shipped to the
OL,8,FUK.
OL,10,FAcross the weekend, prayers have taken
OL,11,Fplace ahead of the official opening.
OL,13,FIt's hoped the temple will also be an
OL,14,Fevents space for people to celebrate
OL,15,Fbirthdays and weddings, and facilitate
OL,16,Fup to 1,000 people.
OL,18,FLeaders and members from the local
OL,19,FSikh Gurdwara, Muslim mosques and
OL,20,FChristian churches have been invited
OL,21,Ffor the official opening ceremony.
